{"word":"ἀκροβολίζομαι","slug":"ἀκροβολίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀκροβολίζομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀκροβόλος'><el>ἀκροβόλος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to throw from afar, to fight with missiles, to skirmish</i>, <el>πρός τινα</el> or <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ἀκρ. ἔπεσι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>—The <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> in <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}